org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.SAM

Interface SaCommStep

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GaCommStep, GaScenario, GaStep, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceUsage, TimedElement, TimedProcessing
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SaCommStepImpl

    public interface SaCommStep
extends GaCommStep
    A representation of the model object 'Sa Comm Step'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Deadline
    • Spare Cap
    • Sch Slack
    • Base Behavioral Feature

    See Also:
    SAMPackage.getSaCommStep()
